{"tid":1376503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"擔遮唔係真係因爲落雨呀！！！","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T10:56:12.000Z","uid":177868,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7492bd5662599e591af1ca63ab2f36802987f941","tid":1376503,"uid":177868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"由琴日發夢元朗都見到原來好多手足都唔識擔遮<br />\n話就話落雨開遮<br />\n擔遮唔係為左遮雨同陽光呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係遮住手足做野 唔好俾天眼/手機影到佢地嘅樣同過程<br />\n屌你成班d遮向天咁擔 左右嘅位全部都空哂 <br />\n咁同無擔有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由而家開始 唔好再全世界向天咁擔<br />\n向左右嘅方向咁拎 </span></strong></span><br />\n務求保護到做緊野嘅手足呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n大家加油 擔遮都好緊要架！！"},{"pid":"0f3a25472a3ee7168fffb5f6fe42b98f60659844","tid":1376503,"uid":177868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a309392c4f9cf8a3f3b753d9867ce5b86098603","tid":1376503,"uid":177868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:47:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14dfcefb46002d8cc5e19d0cc3144fa33f214080","tid":1376503,"uid":177868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32fc9270043759113cdea129aae3ebee05376fe3","tid":1376503,"uid":177868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ae144debdead0f2cf6395766893b00a02d595e0","tid":1376503,"uid":177868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:48:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fcb3c720af4f89a09ed3d58b80dcbcf37982345","tid":1376503,"uid":177868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:49:06.000Z","msg":"推爆佢呀"},{"pid":"6bb706859d0079401b837d49f6373694bdb2c34c","tid":1376503,"uid":177868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:49:16.000Z